ww.hazegray.org/danfs/submar/ss284.txt | accessdate = 4 January 2012 }}</ref>\n}}\n{{shipwreck list item\n|ship={{ship|German trawler|V 1415 Azimuth||2}}\n|flag={{navy|Nazi Germany}}\n|desc=The naval trawler/''[[Vorpostenboot]]'' was lost on this date.<ref name=\"ReferenceC\">{{cite web |url=http://www.navypedia.org/ships/germany/ger_conc_fpv.htm |title=Auxiliary patrols and minesweepers converted from fishing vessels in WWII, Germany |publisher=Navypedia |accessdate=14 March 2017}}</ref>\n}}\n{{shipwreck list item\n|ship={{ship|German trawler|V 1416||2}}\n|flag={{navy|Nazi Germany}}\n|desc=World War II: The ''[[Vorpostenboot]]'' was sunk at IJmuiden in an air raid by Martin B-26 Marauder aircraft of the United States Eighth Air Force.<ref name=seekrieg194403/> }}\n{{shipwreck list end}}\n\n==27 March==\n{{shipwreck list begin |date=27 March 1944 |sort=}}\n{{shipwreck list item\n|ship={{ship|German landing craft|F 609C2||2}}\n|flag={{navy|Nazi Germany}}\n|desc=The [[F-lighter|MFP-C2 landing craft]] was sunk on this date.<ref name=\"MFP landing craft, Germany\">{{cite web |url=http://www.navypedia.org/ships/germany/ger_amph_mfp.htm |title=MFP landing craft, Germany |publisher=Navypedia |accessdate=2 March 2016}}</ref>\n}}\n{{shipwreck list item\n|ship={{ship|German landing craft|F 4706||2}}\n|flag={{navy|Nazi Germany}}\n|desc=The [[F-lighter|MZ-A landing craft]] was sunk on this date.<ref name=\"ReferenceH\">{{cite web |url=http://www.navypedia.org/ships/germany/ger_amph_mz.htm |title=MZ type small landing craft, Germany |publisher=Navypedia |accessdate=3 March 2016}}</ref>\n}}\n{{shipwreck list item\n|ship={{ship|German landing craft|F 4795||2}}\n|flag={{navy|Nazi Germany}}\n|desc=The [[F-lighter|MZ-B landing craft]] was sunk on this date.<ref name=\"ReferenceH\">{{cite web |url=http://www.navypedia.org/ships/germany/ger_amph_mz.htm |title=MZ type small landing craft, Germany |publisher=Navypedia |accessdate=3 March 2016}}</ref>\n}}\n{{shipwreck list item\n|ship={{s